data.description: This complete remodel in the highly sought after Holly Oaks community is a must see! This gorgeous corner lot home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1390sf and includes all new gourmet kitchen with shaker cabinets, granite counter-tops and stainless steel appliances. New hardwood flooring throughout the living, dining, kitchen and hallway lead to the remodeled guest bath with contemporary shaker vanity, granite top, tile floors and bath surround. All bedrooms include plush new carpet, and the master bedroom hosts a brand new private master en-suite with walk in closet. New windows, paint, light/plumbing fixtures and driveway leading to the 1 car attached garage top off this masterpiece. Owner occupants only please.
